CoinJar,is,a,digital,currency,wallet,that,aims,to,bridge,the,gap,between,fiat,and,alternative,currencies,Coinjar,Checkout,offers,same,day,transaction,settlement,accurate,exchange,rates,a,fee,and,charge,back,rate,and,allows,users,to,accept,payment,in,Bitcoin,as,well,as,other,currencies,The,CoinJar,Checkout,API,provides,functionality,for,merchants,and,vendors,to,accept,payments,and,settle,transaction,in,local,currencies,as,well,as,customize,the,interface,on,third,party,websites